    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes the culture and style of the inhabitants of the state of South Australia. It is well known for its production of toas, figurative direction-markers. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
